{"tid":778882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貝碧嘉襲港】或打到正！料西南100公里掠過並再增強","createTime":"2018-08-14T04:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T05:15:11.000Z","uid":44562,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8adb4d92ffa50580a683a92ff8b77c6895d9ede0","tid":778882,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180814/58560424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F58560424&d=8wRfes4BNiqzHQc1cLrktk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4d227fe5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F58560424&h=a3d287f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180814/58560424</a><br />\n<br />\n日前由本港以西300公里外，東移至本港以南200公里內的風暴「貝碧嘉」，今早開始緩慢改向北移，稍後將靠近珠江口一帶，與其相關的雨帶會為本港帶來狂風驟雨，天文台在今早5時20分，改發3號強風信號，預計貝碧嘉稍後逐漸拐彎向西移，並繼續增強，最大機會在今晚至明早，以強烈熱帶風暴的級別，於本港西南100公里左右掠過，可算是正面襲港。<br />\n<br />\n民間氣象組織「地下天文台」指，官方有參考的歐洲超級電腦（ECMWF），預測貝碧嘉明日會於香港以西100公里內登陸，靠近珠江口一帶，將對港澳地區帶來一定威脅，香港天氣會逐漸轉壞，風力增強。值得一提的是，貝碧嘉這風暴名字正是由澳門提供，意指澳門人喜愛吃的、可於澳門葡國餐廳找到的牛奶布丁。"},{"pid":"ea8afc31e640db10674c6e227e9b13be9a579776","tid":778882,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aae8b111af9363c0b7dd836f519ece32a82b6fa","tid":778882,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"蘋果燈走左個風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad5350dc41051b321476c92bfaaf91b787dc5c1","tid":778882,"uid":60545,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTim